415
00:24:28,366 --> 00:24:30,398
"This is a work of fiction and any
similarities between the names of
characters or organizations in this story
and actual names are entirely coincidental."

416
00:24:31,232 --> 00:24:33,101
Your name?

417
00:24:33,101 --> 00:24:34,902
Yuko Murai.

418
00:24:34,902 --> 00:24:37,271
You hate him?

419
00:24:37,271 --> 00:24:40,541
My father trusted him.

420
00:24:40,541 --> 00:24:43,511
He really relied on him
for emotional support...

421
00:24:43,511 --> 00:24:46,447
And yet, from the start, that man...

422
00:24:46,447 --> 00:24:48,316
Your wish?

423
00:24:48,316 --> 00:24:50,918
Banish him to Hell for me!

424
00:24:50,918 --> 00:24:54,689
Your grievance has been heard.

425
00:24:54,689 --> 00:24:55,953
Next time, "Kind Neighbor."

